name: Lotus Pod Leaf Pendant
description:
Copper wire, cut, shaped, soldered, hammered and antiqued, set against art paper, filled with a slice of red lotus pod, set with resin and filled in on the back for an enclosed pendant.

Each Lotus Pod Leaf Pendant is slightly different due the differences in nature and the handmade technique. You will receive 1 leaf which measures approximately 1.5" in length.

name: Warriors Cross - Fused Fine Silver on Copper
description:
An 18 gauge copper cross with scalloped edges, heated to a blazing orange, fused with fine silver for a reticulated shibouchi appearance, pickled, cleaned, tumbled, antiqued, brushed with steel wool and tumbled again for a burnished shine.

Each has unique markings of liquid like silver on its surface and the pendant measures 1.5" in length by 1" wide.

You receive 1 - Warriors Cross Pendant in this listing. Please allow (and celebrate!) slight differences in your fused silver cross.

name: 3prs Ant. Copper Swirl Ear Wires
description:
Add a decorative touch to your hand crafted earrings with these artfully swirled, antiqued copper ear wires!

Measuring approx. 17mm in length with the swirl at 4mm, the ear wires are crafted from 20 gauge pure copper wire. the wire is measured, cut, filed, shaped, hammered, antiqued, polished and finally tumbled to strengthen the metal.

You receive *3* pairs of Antiqued Copper Swirl Ear Wires in this listing. Please allow for slight variations in your ear wires as these are 100% handmade. These are made to order and ship within 1 week of your payment.

Are you worried about base metals in your ear holes or that of your customers? I dip all my handmade copper ear wires in a lacquer that forms a barrier between that of the base metal and the wearer, making these beautiful ear wires an affordable option to gold filled or fine silver.

name: Burmese Replica Coin in Verdigris
description:
A 1" heavy, cast brass pendant made to replicate ancient Burmese coins, treated with several layers of a special verdigris patina on both sides, sanded to reveal the metals texture, sealed in lacquer and finally rubbed with preservation wax for added durability.

You receive 1 - Burmese Replica Coin in this listing. Please allow for variations in the patina and distressing patterns.

name: Ginkgo Leaf in Golden Peridot Pendant
description:
A die cut ginkgo leaf in 18 gauge copper is hammered with my favorite texture hammer, drilled, the edges filed, tumbled and heat treated with a translucent peridot green. The leaf is then touched up with opal powder, sealed with a satin lacquer and rubbed with a preservation wax for added durability.

You receive *1* - 34mm long Ginkgo Leaf in this listing. Please allow for variations in your handmade item.
